<pb facs="1361314" n="1"/>
<lb/><opener><salute>Viro Doctissimo et Celeberrimo <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Ante quindecim dies vestr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">litter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>die</expan></choice> <date when="1715-12-28">28 <abbr>Xbris</abbr></date> dat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/>secure ad me pervenerunt. Vidi doctissimam tuam
         <lb/><rs type="biblio">responsionem</rs> ad ea qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <abbr>D.</abbr> Comes <rs key="pers_DE-588-109091766X" type="person">Riccatus</rs> inseruit <rs type="biblio">To<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mo XXI Diarii Italici <abbr>Art.</abbr> 8</rs>; eamque <rs type="biblio">responsionem</rs>
<lb/>statim in italicam linguam verti ita ut ipsam
         <lb/>paratam habeam pro proximo Tomo Diarii nos<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tri, cui inseri curabo etsi <rs key="pers_DE-588-1037587715" type="person">Diarii editores</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-109091766X" type="person">Riccati</rs>
<lb/>sint valde Amici. Gaudeo de tua responsione, sine
         <lb/>qua <rs key="pers_DE-588-109091766X" type="person">Riccatus</rs> summa cum arrogantia multa iac<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tasset adversus Te. Tibi maximas ago gratias pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice>
         <lb/>iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad me scribere voluisti ad multas meas di<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>fficultates auferendas, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi occurebant in
         <lb/>lectione eorum qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Insignis Mathematicus <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Pa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>truus tuus Johannes</rs> iam pridem publici iuris fe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cit. Me igitur Tibi maxime obstrictum profi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>teor, speroque me<del> tuum</del> vestrum futurum fore
         <lb/>discipulum saltem si <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs> venies ad implen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dam Cathedram, pro qu<unclear>a</unclear> adhuc sperare audeo:
         <lb/>etenim post mensem circiter erit facta totalis
         <lb/>mutatio Personarum in Magistratu <abbr>Illustr.</abbr> et <abbr>Ex<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cell.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatorum</rs> <rs type="organisation"><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavini</rs> Archilycei</rs>: fact<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
         <lb/>autem mutatione Personarum confido de
         <lb/>tua promotione ad eandem Cathedram,
         <pb facs="1361315" n="2"/>
<lb/>quam ut obtineas mea officia quotidi<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> repeto,
   <lb/>rogoque etiam <abbr>D.</abbr> Comitem <rs key="pers_DE-588-118642286" type="person">Schulenburgium</rs>
<lb/>ut me adiuvet suis officiis postquam hac de re
            <lb/>ad me <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">scripsit</rs> etiam <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118571249" type="person">Leibnitius</rs>/rs Vir
         <lb/>summi nominis. Saltem post finem futur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/><date>Quadragesimae</date> ultimam responsionem ad Te 
         <lb/>mittam de <choice><sic>nogotio</sic><corr>negotio</corr></choice> <rs type="organisation">Cathedr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Patavin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>. <rs key="biblio_4RTURNJD" type="biblio">Trac<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tatum</rs> de Lingua Tuscana <rs key="pers_DE-588-120752840" type="person">Benedicti Buommatei</rs>,
         <lb/>et <rs key="pers_DE-588-11757645X" type="person">Gulielmini</rs> <rs key="biblio_4RTURNJD" type="biblio">tractatum</rs> de Mensura aqua<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum fluentium prima occasione ad Te mit<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tam Vir Clarissime.</p> <closer><salute>Tu interim vale et me
         <lb/>amare perge.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Ven<subst><del>i</del><add>e</add></subst>tiis</rs> <choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>die</expan></choice> <date when="1716-01-24">24 Januarii
            <lb/>1715 more veneto
            <lb/>1716 more Imperii</date></dateline><note type="editorial">Das Datum ist auf zwei Zeilen ähnlich einem Bruch aufgeteilt.<!-- evtl. auf Darstellungsebene eine Lösung finden, z.B. mit <p> --></note></closer>
</div></body></text></TEI>